to compile and install:
1. ant -f gbuild.xml gwt-compile
2. ant
3. ant install

4. Now add the gwt servlet to the platform web.xml:

  <servlet>
    <servlet-name>gechoServlet</servlet-name>
    <servlet-class>org.pentaho.samples.gecho.server.GEchoServiceImpl</servlet-class>
  </servlet>
  
  <servlet-mapping>
    <servlet-name>gechoServlet</servlet-name>
    <url-pattern>/gecho/echo</url-pattern>
  </servlet-mapping>
  
5. Now drop the gecho-plugin-*.jar into the platform WEB-INF/lib directory and (re)start the Pentaho BI Server
